skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: gym motivator
des: We all have reasons not to go to the gym. Too tired, too busy, too "sore" from last time, not feeling motivated, would rather hang out and drink wine... the list goes on. Try your excuses on this Gym Motivator. She plays the role of rational voice that reminds you what's best for you. Because sometimes, hearing your excuses out loud is the best way to hear how silly they are.
priv: Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
